      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes a modification to the IETF procedures to allow an escape from a situation where the existing procedures are not working or do not seem to apply.  This document specifies an Internet Best Current Practices for the Internet Community, and requests discussion and suggestions for improvements.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
